      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "value": "<p>This short staff ends in reconfigurable wrench-like prongs suited for operating on heavy machinery, sawing through debris, and incapacitating robots gone haywire. Each crisis wrench has specially fitted compartments along its length that stores an @Compendium[sfrpg.equipment.T9nRPwJibhTuMjkp]{engineering kit} (Core Rulebook 221), and all crisis wrenches other than the tinker-class model also house an engineering specialty tool kit selected when purchasing the weapon. These kits are included in the weapon&rsquo;s price and bulk.</p>\n<p><strong>Additional Special Details</strong></p>\n<p>professional (maintenance worker)</p>",
      "unidentified": ""
    },
